  "title": "💙 Charity Ambassador (Fundraising Team) — Make an Impact 💙",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>EMINENCE ORGANIZATION is a dynamic events and sales company that thrives on creativity and energy. Our young and vibrant team brings fresh ideas to the table, ensuring every project is as bold and exciting as the next. Here, we don’t just market products or drive sales—we create moments that stick. Let’s make magic happen!</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Join our Charity Fundraising Team to represent nonprofit organizations, raise awareness, and contribute directly to social causes through face-to-face outreach. No prior experience is required.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Engage with members of the public to clearly explain charity campaigns and increase awareness</li><li>Collect donations by effectively communicating the impact of causes such as children’s welfare, healthcare, education, and community support</li><li>Participate actively in roadshows, events, and outreach activities to promote fundraising efforts</li><li>Collaborate closely with team members to support campaign goals and maintain a positive, mission-driven environment</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Demonstrate compassion and genuine care for community welfare</li><li>Communicate clearly and persuasively to advocate for social causes</li><li>Maintain an energetic and positive attitude when approaching and interacting with people</li></ul>",
